{"tid":2391728,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"紐約香港學生「擁抱」後遺症 創作遊戲影射「反送中」","createTime":"2021-02-02T11:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T12:38:17.000Z","uid":321748,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7da65b1aa48530826a5335192130c09a18973e7a","tid":2391728,"uid":321748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T11:25:13.000Z","msg":"（北美通訊）香港在2019年經歷「反送中」社會運動，掀起的餘波仍然在盪漾。跟很多香港人一樣，海外港人即使無法身在現場，也出現創傷後遺症。兩名在紐約修讀藝術的香港學生，計劃製作以香港為背景的電腦遊戲《集體後遺症》，期望以遊戲作為媒介，感染和連繫不同種族文化。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210202/WOYMZIZZZ5H5RD3PBD2DHV2B6Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210202%2FWOYMZIZZZ5H5RD3PBD2DHV2B6Y%2F&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BInMh2OwnA7FCi%2BsKpr4SDY%3D&h=dcb11527\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210202%2FWOYMZIZZZ5H5RD3PBD2DHV2B6Y%2F&h=f1017a50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210202/WOYMZIZZZ5H5RD3PBD2DHV2B6Y/</a>"},{"pid":"e1a317dfde32f8cb0120d4a7b1d486c496cdd00b","tid":2391728,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T12:38:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}